joelib2.data
Class BasicIsotopeHolder

java.lang.Object
  joelib2.data.IdentifierSoftDefaultSystem
      joelib2.data.AbstractDataHolder
          joelib2.data.BasicIsotopeHolder
All Implemented Interfaces:
IdentifierHardDependencies, IdentifierSoftDependencies, IsotopeHolder
public class BasicIsotopeHolder
extends AbstractDataHolder
implements IdentifierHardDependencies, IsotopeHolder

Isotope element table. The definition file can be defined in the joelib2.data.JOEIsotopeTable.resourceFile property in the BasicPropertyHolder. The BasicResourceLoader loads the joelib2.properties file for default.

Default:
joelib2.data.JOEIsotopeTable.resourceFile=joelib2/data/plain/isotope.txt
